solution:
We have \begin{align*}
2^{2001}\times5^{1950}\div4^{27}&= 2^{2001}\div2^{54}\times5^{1950} \\
&= 2^{1947}\times5^{1950}\\
&= (2\times5)^{1947}\times5^3 \\
&= 125\times10^{1947}
